GSP is in pilot-scale development toward formal standardization.
This repository contains engineering protocol artifacts and supporting technical specifications used for validation, scale-up, and interoperability testing.
Scope

Included:
Glass Substrate Protocol (.gsp) files
GSP Technical Specifications (TECH-SPECS)
Pilot metadata and validation artifacts

Excluded:
Certification claims
Compliance assertions
Legal or regulatory determinations
Non-Certification Notice
Protocols in this repository do not constitute certification, warranty, or compliance claims.

No protocol is “GSP-compliant” until formal standard adoption and certification mechanisms are activated.

Governance Context
Glass Substrate Protocol (GSP) is being developed with the intent to transition into a certifiable external standard. Governance, certification, and branding are managed separately and are not active at the pilot stage.

Versioning
All .gsp files are versioned and immutable once tagged
Git LFS is mandatory for protocol files
Pilot releases are tagged per tool and lot
